Salawa akh can be found inside the Sophanem Slayer Dungeon. Level 105 Slayer is required to deal damage to and kill the monster. A Feather of Ma'at is required to complete each kill. Sumona has a high chance of assigning them.[1]

They are the only soul devourers to not possess a mechanic of any sort.
